With the Spotify app, you can explore an extensive library of music and podcasts for free. Curate the best playlists and stream millions of free songs, albums and original podcasts on your mobile or tablet. Subscribe to Spotify Premium to download and listen offline wherever you are, and unlock our catalogue of audiobooks.

Why choose Spotify as your go-to music and podcast app? Here, you can:
• Listen to over 100 million songs and 6 million podcast titles
• Explore our selection of specially-crafted artist playlists
• Easily search for your favourite songs, albums, artists and podcasts
• Discover personalised music recommendations tailored to your unique taste
• Subscribe to your favourite free podcasts so you never miss an episode and even curate your own podcast library

Spotify Free is more than a music player – find the sounds that you love and stream music and podcasts online for free. Enjoy personalised playlists or curate and share your own, discover the hottest new releases, explore upcoming events from your favourites and more.

• Stream millions of free songs and podcasts
• Create playlists with your favourite music
• Share songs and playlists with friends and family (feature restrictions may apply in some regions)
• Discover personalised playlists made just for you, and collaborate on playlists with your friends
• Enjoy your personal Discover Weekly playlist every week
• Stay in the know with the Release Radar and New Music Friday playlists
• Find nearby events and gigs by your favourite artists
• See your most played songs, genres, artists and more with yearly Spotify Wrapped
• Stream music across your devices with Spotify
• Use Spotify Connect and enjoy listening on smart speakers, desktop, laptop, smart TV, Chromecast, PlayStation®, Xbox®, smartwatch, in your car and more – limited number of device models apply

Spotify Premium – a great way to enjoy the benefits of an offline music player and stream music without Wi-Fi. By pressing download, you can access your songs, playlists, podcasts and audiobooks offline, wherever you are.
• Listen to music, podcasts and audiobooks – all in one place
• Ad-free music listening: enjoy your music with no ad interruptions
• Enjoy full on-demand playback
• Audiobooks in Premium are currently available in the UK, US, Australia, Ireland, New Zealand and Canada. Discover 250,000+ audiobook titles with 15 hours/month of available listening for Premium Individual subscribers and Duo & Family plan managers.
• Superior sound quality on supported devices
• AI DJ: a personalised guide that knows your music taste so well that it can choose what to play for you
• Enjoy on desktop, mobile phone, tablet, computer, smartwatch and in your car
• Listen and control the listening session together by hosting a Jam in real time with friends
• Download songs, podcasts and audiobooks for offline listening without an Internet connection
• No contract required – cancel your subscription whenever you want

Spotify lets you play music wherever you are. Listen to your favourite songs and discover new music, podcasts and audiobooks with the Spotify app!

Now! We proudly present ASMR Musi, the ultimate solution for your music playback needs.

The app brings together a variety of soundscapes such as the crunch of chewing, the rustle of turning pages, the sound of soft whispers, the warmth of wood, the crinkling of packaging, the melodies of instruments, the click of nails, the scribbles of pens, and more.

Each auditory selection has been carefully curated to provide the best relaxation experience.
The app has an intuitive and easy-to-use interface that easily guides users through various sound categories and allows users to save bookmarks based on their personal preferences. For those who want to keep their unique auditory moments forever, the in-app recording feature is a perfect solution. It allows users to capture, edit recordings, and manage their audio library by removing outdated tracks, ensuring a fresh and tailored listening experience at all times.

edjing Mix is a virtual DJ pro that allows you to mix music like a true DJ. With its turntable interface and DG technology, you can easily create mashups and song mixes like a pro. Whether you're a seasoned DJ or just looking for a fun DJ game to try, edjing Mix is the perfect app for you.

Access millions of tracks coming from Beatport, SoundCloud Go +, iTunes and your Cloud sources, and remix in an instant with more than 20 DJ fx and features. Not to mention the sampler and the hardware integration to go even further.

* ‘edjing Mix offers the same capability of a pro DJ software except with the convenience of being on a device that fits in a pocket.’ - DJ Tech Tools
* 'A super portable digital setup' - DJ Worx

ENDLESS MUSIC LIBRARY

- Mix with more than 70 million tracks thanks to your musical libraries
- Compatibility with Beatport, SoundCloud Go +, iTunes, Google Drive, Dropbox, Files, iCloud Drive, files and more to come !*
- Dedicated section "My sets" to retrieve your playlists, sets and recorded mixes
- Smart search feature and queue system
- Library analysis to save the BPM of your local tracks
- Advanced sorting: ABC, BPM, or Time
- iPad dedicated design: displays the music library, the queue and the turntables, with drag & drop gestures


ALL THE MUST-HAVE DJ TOOLS

- automatic BPM detection
- SMART EQ: instantly isolate vocals, percussions and instruments of any tracks
- manual adjustment of the BPM of your tracks (Tap BPM)
- continuous sync between your tracks
- little audio spectrum to navigate in your music
- wide audio spectrum for optimised beat detection
- pro audio FX: Echo, Flanger, Reverse, Filter
- audio FX expansion (in-app purchase): Roll, Roll Filter, Steel, Gate, Double Beat, Phaser, Color Noise, Beatgrid, Band pass, Band stop, Reverb
- loops: from 1/64 to 128, or customizable
- cue point on the main interface
- set up to 8 Hot Cues on each deck
- automated audio FX sync on the BPM (loop, cue, seek)
- EQ three bands and Gain
- Smart Volume that automatically adjusts the volume and gain of the two tracks playing
- pitch control and key lock
- Pre-cueing stereo with headphones (in-app purchase)
- Automix
- a 'Slip' mode for Loops and Scratch
- HD recording in .aiff format
- set the vinyl inertia, and the starting speed of the vinyl
- crossfader curve adjustement
- 4 skins for your turntables (in-app purchase): Diamond, Gold, Neon, Metal
- Apple watch: access the BPM & 4 DJ effects, and start your transitions
- intuitive interface with direct and quick access to all the essential features
- apply two audio FX at the same time on each deck
- reorder the FX lists to customize the panel as it suits you best

# DJ SCHOOL
- The first DJ MASTER CLASS on mobile with video and exercises to practice. Discover the DJ World and DJ Basics with DJ Carlo Atendido. 
- TRAINING: Practice mixing through simple lessons covering all the basics

HARDWARE INTEGRATION
- compatible with your time coded and standard audio vinyls
- MIDI support with DDJ-200

MUSIC SOURCES INFORMATION
- No recording available for streamed songs. Streaming service availability and pricing may vary depending on country, currency and service. 
- edjing Mix can not access tracks from the Apple Music, Spotify or Deezer streaming services.
- To use songs from iCloud in edjing Mix you need to download them first via the Music app. DRM-protected songs are not supported.


The Pro subscription allows you access all the present and upcoming Pro features such as Pre-cueing, Smart EQ, Automix, Double FX. It gives you access to all the Pro and regularly updated content: edjing Tracks catalog, DJ School Master Classes, audios samples.

Amplify your imagination. Powered by the world’s most advanced AI music model, Suno transforms your ideas into songs—no instruments needed, just your creative vision. Whether you’re a shower-singer, aspiring songwriter, or charting artist, Suno empowers you to create and discover music like never before.

Generate music from prompts, images, or videos with the world’s best AI music model:
• Transform your ideas into fully-produced songs and beats with a single prompt. Create 10 songs or beats per day at no cost.
• Inspiration begins with you. Write a text prompt like "Create a rap song about walking my dog," sing a melody, hum a tune, or tap out a beat.
• Record or upload audio to personalize your music, or generate songs from images and videos.

Write original lyrics with effortlessly:
• Whether you're in your feels with emotional ballads, hyped on energetic rap verses, or hooked on catchy pop, our lyrics generator and AI songwriter helps you craft custom lyrics that match your style and creative vision.

Create playlists for every mood and moment:
• Curate your personal AI music library and organize your favorite tracks, beats, and instrumentals into playlists you can revisit anytime.
• Manage your AI songs, view track details, and fine-tune your playlists—your music making journey is uniquely yours with Suno.

Discover new music and connect with artists:
• Stay inspired by listening to tracks created by other users and explore the best AI music across genres like rock, rap, hip hop, pop, and more.
• Find fresh favorites by browsing trending music and follow artists to stay connected.
• Discover new voice styles, AI covers, rising talent, and beat makers from around the world.

Music has no boundaries at Suno. Anything you imagine can take shape as a song to share. Whether you're taking your first steps in music making or chasing your next hit, infinite possibilities begin with a simple prompt in our AI song generator. Feeling pro? Take full creative control: adjust vocals, tweak structure, fine-tune melodies, and edit every detail to your vision.

Suno is how imagination becomes music, and music becomes yours.

The Real Piano provides all the tools necessary to master the art of playing piano and electronic keyboard on your smartphone or tablet. Now you can easily play any music, anywhere! Feel the sensation of playing piano or electronic keyboard in a real band!

What is a piano?
A piano is a musical instrument that produces sound by striking strings with hammers. It's known for its wide range and versatility, making it suitable for various music genres.

Haven't learned to play the piano yet?
Real Piano offers multiple video lessons to support you, along with a variety of loops for interactive play-along experiences.

Don't have access to a grand piano or an electronic keyboard? No problem! 
Real Piano provides a diverse range of instruments with high-quality sounds, enabling you to play any song you desire!

You don't need a physical piano or a digital keyboard to learn to play!
Real Piano is an ideal choice for practicing or playing the piano quietly, without causing disturbance or requiring extensive space. Enjoy the freedom to practice piano anywhere you like!

Show your friends how good you are at playing piano!
Share videos of your performances with friends and on social media!

The Real Piano app allows both children and adults to learn the piano while having fun and enhancing their cognitive and motor skills. This piano game will stimulate your musical talent, making it easy to learn as if using a real piano instrument.

So, what are you waiting for? Become a pianist today!


Explore the features of Real Piano:

- 100 piano lessons: Learn to play piano with our lessons.

- Full 7 octaves Scale: Explore the entire keyboard.

- Keyboard and Chord Mode: Switch between playing on a real keyboard and playing chords effortlessly.

- Adjustable Scale Size: Customize the keyboard to your preference.

- Piano Chords Library: Access over 1500 chords.

- Studio Audio Quality: Enjoy crystal-clear sound.

- A Diverse Range of Instruments: acoustic pianos, synthesizers, electric pianos, organs, wind instruments, string instruments, guitars, basses and other ethnic instruments.

- New Instruments Weekly: Keep your sound fresh.

- Recording Mode: Record your tunes and share them on social media.

- Interactive Loops: Play along with professionally crafted loops.

- MIDI Support: Connect your MIDI devices for enhanced control.

- Universal Compatibility: Works seamlessly on all screen resolutions, from smartphones to tablets (HD images).

- Free App: No hidden costs.

- Delay-Free Audio: Enjoy seamless sound.
